format
login usr1 usr1
create note
open note rw
write 3 private data
close 3
logout
login usr2 usr2
open /home/usr1/note r
logout
login root root
acl grant /home/usr1 usr2 x path_prefix=/home/usr1
acl grant /home/usr1/note usr2 r path_prefix=/home/usr1
logout
login usr2 usr2
open /home/usr1/note r
read 3 64
group create readers
group grant readers to usr2 with grant option path_prefix=/home/usr1
group list
fsck
exit
